CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 8, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "Duquesne Community Chorus Holds Concert In Braddock - Pictured here is the Duquesne Community Chorus which held its first major concert in Braddock last week. Director of the chorus is John Blakey.  The concert was given at Carnegie Music hall in Duquesne. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the Duquesne Community Chorus gathered on stage in Carnegie Music Hall, Duquesne
